query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('c#',
'cartography',
'commas',
'csv',
'dem',
'google-earth-engine',
'qgis-3',
'sentence')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'electronics',
'english',
'gis',
'salesforce')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Fanatic',
'Tag Editor',
'Talkative',
'Tenacious')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
